---
title: Beef-Pork Meatballs & Veggie Couscous with Herby Mayo & Almonds
description: We love a supreme double protein combo. Both beef and pork come together in the shape of meatballs to fill up a roast veggie
couscous. The double garnish too is a real treat, there’s roasted almonds and a dollop of herby mayo. Sometimes more is good!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-pork-meatballs-roast-veggie-couscous-237efe3d.jpg
